{"type": "article", "id": 2705, "title": "早安摩卡咖啡壶套装", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-08T07:43:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052324435CnkTJizgSDquKYt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t挪威奥斯陆设计师 Andersson &amp; Voll 设计了一款早安摩卡咖啡壶套装，咖啡壶采用了当下流行的明亮黄色作为主色调，配有大理石板雕刻而成的小型灶台。设计灵感来源于分层式的日本传统茶壶，大理石灶台的材质选取，强调了其具有雕塑般的品质。这款套装还包括采用混凝土制造的可用灯泡进行加热的咖啡机，和一个水壶。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232441e8hS9GQH4xctm6No.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232441Ii2V6gNWBTdqPRvS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232442fkPexqKVEyWM4Gn7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}